  "2026-06-05T14:58:16.580Z",maintainer-agent,"BUNDLE COMPLETE (working tree only; NOT committed/pushed per run constraint). Delivered via 2 specialized sub-agents (mcp-platform-subagent, sdk-docs-subagent) on disjoint file sets + orchestrator. Closed 8 children: pm-hywv+pm-77t3 (narrow MCP tools pm_notes/pm_learnings/pm_deps, 18→21 tools), pm-qxwu (typo-swallow hardening: TOOL_DECLARED_KEYS + structuredContent.warnings + stderr + did-you-mean, pm_run exempt), pm-fd8n (pm_run action list derived from PM_TOOL_ACTIONS), pm-r9sz (PM_TOOL_PARAMETERS_SCHEMA_VERSION/_MAJOR constants + bound assertion sites), pm-kl11 (tests/integration/mcp-handshake.spec.ts), pm-te9x + pm-k5r6 (docs/EXTENSIONS.md: capture_level semantics + dual write-path contract). VERIFICATION: clean build, 139 files / 2309 tests pass, 100% coverage (stmts/branch/func/lines), manual sandbox MCP test (tools/list=21, narrow tools functional, typo warning fires, unknown-tool error, pm contracts schema_version=4.0.2). FOLLOW-UP filed: pm-3puw (MCP stdio server handles JSON-RPC lines concurrently → pipelined same-item mutations lock-conflict; pre-existing, low severity, out of scope). Plan left open as the durable session record (per pm-z5nb precedent for coordination plans)."
  "2026-06-05T15:22:17.934Z",codex-coverage-contracts,"Coverage/contracts verification sub-agent evidence: inspected dirty diff for pm-d6kq/MCP/SDK contracts. Verified package scripts include contracts:update/contracts:check, CI static gate calls pnpm contracts:check, scripts/contracts-snapshot.mjs runs dist/cli.js contracts --full --json against tests/fixtures/contracts/full.json, and docs/TESTING.md documents the update/check flow. Focused verification passed: pnpm build; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts tests/integration/mcp-handshake.spec.ts tests/unit/shared-helpers.spec.ts (3 files, 41 tests); pnpm contracts:check. GitHub read-only checks: no open PRs, no open issues, no open Dependabot alerts via gh api GET, pnpm audit clean; pnpm outdated reports only commander 14.0.3 -> 15.0.0, already tracked by pm-7j8t. Gap: pm-d6kq is not ready to close until untracked scripts/contracts-snapshot.mjs and tests/fixtures/contracts/full.json are included in the PR; otherwise a fresh checkout would miss the gate and/or fixture even though this dirty worktree passes."
  "2026-06-05T15:24:32.589Z",maintainer-agent,"GitHub/Nightly follow-up: reproduced failing Nightly compatibility gate locally (expected legacy comments to survive current build read path). Root cause was scripts/release/compatibility-check.mjs rewriting a legacy markdown item from compact pm get output, which omits heavy collections after token-efficiency changes. Fixed by using legacy get --depth full before the markdown/YAML-wrapper conversion. Evidence: pnpm build && node scripts/release/compatibility-check.mjs --json passed against published base_version 2026.6.5; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts passed (33 tests)."
  "2026-06-05T15:28:42.941Z",maintainer-agent,"Final run evidence (no commit/push): sub-agents checked GitHub/security/contracts; no open PRs/issues, no vulnerabilities, commander 15 remains tracked by pm-7j8t. Fixed Nightly Validation failure locally by changing compatibility-check legacy fixture to use get --depth full; node scripts/release/compatibility-check.mjs --json passes against base_version 2026.6.5. Package-owned changelog regenerated and pnpm changelog:pm:check passes with pm-changelog 2026.6.5-1. Gates passed: pnpm build, pnpm contracts:check, node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts, node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (139 files, 2314 tests, 100%), pnpm typecheck, pnpm quality:static, pnpm security:scan, pnpm audit --audit-level low, pm health --check-only --summary --json. pm validate ok with pre-existing resolution warnings only (51 older closed items missing resolution metadata, no history drift). Manual temp directory smoke passed: init/create/comments/notes/learnings/test run/contracts/health with schema_version 4.0.2 and 75 actions. Remote note: git fetch shows origin/main advanced to bb74cef/v2026.6.5; local dirty main is behind and should be rebased/merged before PR prep."
  "2026-06-05T15:32:14.835Z",diff-hygiene-subagent,"Diff/tracker hygiene review (no source edits): git diff --check clean; no live secrets/private host data found in dirty/untracked paths (matches were docs redaction examples and contract regexes). Risks: .agents/pm/extensions/pm-changelog is deleted while .managed-extensions.json says pm-changelog 2026.6.5-1 is installed; likely accidental managed-extension churn unless intentionally excluded/restored before PR. .agents/pm/runtime/*.json untracked cache files are generated local churn and should not be included. pm-d6kq adequately links contracts snapshot files/docs/tests, but scripts/contracts-snapshot.mjs and tests/fixtures/contracts/full.json are still untracked in this worktree. pm-3puw adequately describes serial MCP queue work. pm-at83 describes the bundle well in comments, but formal files/docs links on the plan are sparse; many plugin/docs/smoke changes are documented via child comments rather than linked metadata."
  "2026-06-05T15:33:27.732Z",github-security-subagent,"GitHub/security/release verification sub-agent evidence (no commit/push/source edits intended). Commands: gh pr list --state open --limit 50 --json ... => 0; gh issue list --state open --limit 100 --json ... => 0; gh run list --limit 30 --json ... showed latest Nightly Validation 27003502016 failed on main bb74cef while latest Auto Release 27000157629 succeeded; gh run view 27003502016 --log-failed => ubuntu Node 20 compatibility migration gate failed: expected legacy comments to survive current build read path; gh run view 26995600561 --log-failed => earlier Auto Release failed sentry-telemetry-gate with 1 high Sentry issue, superseded by later successful scheduled Auto Release; gh api dependabot alerts open => 0; vulnerability-alerts endpoint => 204 enabled; secret-scanning alerts open => 0; security-advisories open => 0; code-scanning alerts unavailable/404 no analysis found plus scope hint; pnpm audit --audit-level moderate and low => no known vulnerabilities; pnpm security:scan => no credential-like secrets detected; pnpm outdated --format json => commander 14.0.3 -> 15.0.0 only, already tracked by pm-7j8t; npm view pm-changelog version + pm package doctor + pnpm changelog:pm:check => pm-changelog 2026.6.5-1 active/current and CHANGELOG unchanged. Local dirty branch check: node scripts/release/compatibility-check.mjs --json passes against base_version 2026.6.5, so remote Nightly failure is actionable until the existing local compatibility-check fix is included in the PR. Release state: v2026.6.5 and npm @unbrained/pm-cli 2026.6.5 are published; local HEAD 5419a815 is behind origin/main bb74cef."
  "2026-06-05T15:34:35.670Z",codex-sdk-continuation,"Continuation evidence (no commit/push): refreshed live state after origin/main advanced to v2026.6.5. Sub-agents verified GitHub/security/release and diff/tracker hygiene. Current local gates passed: pnpm build; pnpm contracts:check; pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog 2026.6.5-1; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts tests/integration/mcp-handshake.spec.ts tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts tests/unit/shared-helpers.spec.ts (74 tests); node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (139 files, 2314 tests, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines); pnpm typecheck; pnpm quality:static; pnpm security:scan; pnpm audit --audit-level low; node scripts/release/compatibility-check.mjs --json; pm health --check-only --summary --json; pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift (known pre-existing 51 resolution warnings only, no history drift); git diff --check. Manual temp-dir smoke passed with isolated PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH: init/create/comments/notes/learnings/test run/contracts/health, schema_version 4.0.2, 89 commands, 75 actions. GitHub: no open PRs/issues/security alerts; latest Auto Release succeeded; latest Nightly Validation failure is reproduced as fixed locally by compatibility-check full-depth legacy fixture change. Hygiene: no secrets found; runtime cache files are generated local files and should not be included; scripts/contracts-snapshot.mjs and tests/fixtures/contracts/full.json remain intentionally untracked until PR prep/staging."
  "2026-06-05T15:37:34.977Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"Continuation start: claimed existing MCP/contracts/platform bundle for PR prep, remote sync, verification refresh, GitHub/security checks, reviewer loop, and merge-closeout. Will preserve existing dirty work and avoid duplicate pm items."
